eral to make regulations prescribing matters, so far as presently relevant, required or permitted by Pt\~8 to be prescribed.  Regulation\~3(1)(d) of the Corporations (Commonwealth Authorities and Officers) Regulations}{\cs21\b\super \chftn {\footnote 
